Text: You sure he did this song?

Yes, he really did sing this song.

Unfortunately this torrent is dead, but you can still get the song from the official Clone High website here:
http://www.clonehighusa.com

It's under downloads, and then Original Songs, 
Episode 2: Marylin Manson Food Pyramid.

Also the complete series of Clone High was released in December of 2007 on DVD.
